{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01EdkjzNckWcYCKyjCUV5sp3","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## STEP 02 — Template Instruction Constraints\n\n### Full A1 Content by Sheet\n\n---\n\n**Sheet: Vendor Analysis Assessment**\n> `Vendor Name`\nColumn header only — no embedded instructions.\n\n---\n\n**Sheet: Top 3 Opportunities**\n> *(empty)*\nNo instructions present in A1.\n\n---\n\n**Sheet: Methodology**\n> *\"Please provide a brief explanation for how you approached working through this. (what was your methodology, prompt(s), tools, etc)\"*\n\n---\n\n**Sheet: CEOCFO Recommendations**\n> *\"Please prepare a short memo (maximum 1 page) summarizing your findings and recommendations to the CEO and CFO.*\n> *Please keep in mind that these are busy people; position your points accordingly, focus on what really matters, and do not exceed the number of pages; do not overemphasize things that are obvious to them but also keep in mind they have many things going on and may not remember immediately certain points.*\n> *Please provide a Google Doc link to your memo below.\"*\n\n---\n\n**Sheet: Config**\n> `Department`\nColumn header only — no embedded instructions.\n\n---\n\n### Constraints Summary\n\n| Sheet | Binding Constraint |\n|---|---|\n| **CEOCFO Recommendations** | Memo must be **maximum 1 page**. Must include a **Google Doc link** below the memo. Tone: executive-level, concise, no over-explanation of obvious points. |\n| **Methodology** | Requires a narrative explanation of methodology, tools, and prompts used. |\n| **Top 3 Opportunities** | No structural constraints specified in A1. |\n| **Vendor Analysis Assessment** | Data sheet — no output format constraints. |\n| **Config** | Reference/lookup sheet — no output constraints. |\n\n### Key constraint for downstream steps\n\nThe **CEOCFO Recommendations** sheet (likely populated in STEP 09) is the most constrained:\n- Hard **1-page limit** — brevity is mandatory, not optional\n- A **Google Doc link** must be placed in that sheet (below the memo text)\n- Framing must be executive-appropriate: lead with what matters, omit the obvious"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":910,"cache_read_input_tokens":15944,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":910,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"22ec7121-f94a-4f75-a15f-c898f36a41cd","uuid":"a0667d92-a03e-4f0a-b584-c021f3750807"}
